  ErrorBoundary + Suspense for loading/error states
- Lit: @lit-labs/router, @lit/context for DI, @lit/task for async data
- ESLint: import-x (ordering/cycles), jsx-a11y (React), lit/wc (Lit)
- Vite: vendor-splitting via `manualChunks`, `lightningcss` for CSS


- `.zsh` extension with `#!/usr/bin/env zsh`
- `setopt ERR_EXIT PIPE_FAIL` at top
- All variables quoted: `"${var}"`
- ShellCheck compliant

